text: What if I know suicide is selfish  but I feel so far gone from any kind of individuality  I don t know what I am because I m dead to myself  My family loves me more than anything I m sure  but we haven t enjoyed our time together in a long time because I m not who I used to be  Most of the time I m a ghost in the room with nothing to contribute because my soul is gone  I don t enjoy anything  At this point I m not sure I have the empathy required to understand how my family might react  Extreme grief for certain  Lifelong pain like I feel now  They don t deserve that My treatment has been ineffective for   years  There s nothing I feel for enough to hang on to I used to cope with drugs and cutting  In   I made a promise to my mom to stop cutting permanently  I intend to keep that promise  There  is nothing else that makes me feel  I have no momey for drugs It is either a  life sentence  for me here on Earth  or I pull the plug and devastate my family  I m done with meds  hospitals  therapists  psychiatrists  etc  They haven t helped  not for lack of trying Hypothetically  what would happen to my   dollars in private and federal student loans if I end my life  How could one dampen the effects of the loss their family would experience   to any extent  I probably sound like an awful person  This just isn t for me  no amount of rewiring of my mind has changed that at all It has occurred to me to stage a sort of going away from my family and manage a move somewhere contact would be limited for a time to let them adjust to life without me before I go for good I ll probably just take the considerate route and put my head down and keep to myself as long as I can  Nightmares gnaw at my composure  though  Every  Single  Night  Traumatic experiences that probably would sound mild to most people eat at me  Dying sounds awful  death sounds blissful
